== 製作 ==
起初電影將由[[史蒂芬·索德柏|史蒂芬·索德柏]]執導，改編劇本交給{{link-en|史考特·Z·伯恩斯|Scott Z. Burns}}負責，並於3月開始發展，2012年時[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]高層希望預算能維持低於6000萬美元，但索德柏覺得要提供20世紀60年代時期的道具這個數目並不夠<ref>{{cite news|title=Steven Soderbergh Spies Other Plans, Won't Direct 'The Man From U.N.C.L.E.'|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/exclusive-steven-soderbergh-opts-out-of-directing-warners-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=indiewire.com|date=2011-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212185321/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/exclusive-steven-soderbergh-opts-out-of-directing-warners-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e|archive-date=2015-02-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2011年11月18日，據《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》，索德柏退出了本片的執導<ref>{{cite news|title=Steven Soderbergh Exits Warner Bros.' 'Man From U.N.C.L.E.'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/steven-soderbergh-man-from-uncle-263592|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2011-11-18|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207224220/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/steven-soderbergh-man-from-uncle-263592|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年3月18日，[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]報導，電影的製作工作再度恢復，並由[[蓋·瑞奇|蓋·瑞奇]]擔任導演<ref name=tom>{{cite news|title=Tom Cruise Eyeing 'The Man From U.N.C.L.E.' With Guy Ritchie At Warner Bros|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/tom-cruise-eyeing-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-with-guy-ritchie-at-warner-bros/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2013-03-18|archive-date=2013-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825100206/http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/tom-cruise-eyeing-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-with-guy-ritchie-at-warner-bros/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月31日，宣布電影將於2013年9月在[[倫敦|倫敦]]和[[義大利|義大利]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=The Man From U.N.C.L.E. Finally Starts Filming in September|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=107240|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=comingsoon.net|date=2013-07-31|archive-date=2013-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130805133419/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=107240|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’ aims to start filming in September|url=http://www.hitfix.com/news/man-from-uncle-aims-to-start-filming-in-september|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=hitfix.com|date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2013-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130809024348/http://www.hitfix.com/news/man-from-uncle-aims-to-start-filming-in-september|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

