|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=slashfilm.com|date=2011-11-10|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119154232/http://www.slashfilm.com/bradley-cooper-steven-soderberghs-man-uncle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年3月18日，[[湯姆·克魯斯|湯姆·克魯斯]]初期被討論將會出演電影中<ref name="tom" />，2013年4月24日， [[艾米·漢默|艾米·漢默]]將飾演第二主角{{link-en|伊利亞·科里亞金|Illya Kuryakin}}，而克魯斯則飾演拿破崙·蘇洛<ref name=Armie>{{cite news|title=‘Lone Ranger’ Armie Hammer To Star With Tom Cruise In ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/lone-ranger-armie-hammer-to-star-with-tom-cruise-in-man-from-u-n-c-l-e/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2013-04-24|archive-date=2013-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130808081859/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/lone-ranger-armie-hammer-to-star-with-tom-cruise-in-man-from-u-n-c-l-e/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。瑞典女演員[[艾莉西亞·薇坎德|艾莉西亞·薇坎德]]於2013年5月8日加入劇組擔任女主角<ref name=Alicia>{{cite news|title=Alicia Vikander Finds Her ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’ for Warners|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/alicia-vikander-man-from-uncle-tom-cruise-1200477208/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=variety.com|date=2013-05-08|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921081506/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/alicia-vikander-man-from-uncle-tom-cruise-1200477208/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年5月23日，克魯斯基於他對《[[不可能的任務：失控國度|不可能的任務：失控國度]]》的出演承諾<ref>{{cite news|title=Tom Cruise Exits 'Man from U.N.C.L.E.' Due to 'Mission: Impossible 5'|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2013/tom-cruise-exits-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-due-to-mission-impossible-5/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=firstshowing.net|date=2013-05-24|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116221220/https://www.firstshowing.net/2013/tom-cruise-exits-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-due-to-mission-impossible-5/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Tom Cruise Exits ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.;’ Warner Bros Recasting For Fall Start|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/shocker-tom-cruise-exits-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2013-05-24|archive-date=2014-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726154748/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/shocker-tom-cruise-exits-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不得已退出電影。改由英國演員[[亨利·卡維爾|亨利·卡維爾]]代替克魯斯擔任主演<ref name="budget"/><ref name=Henry>{{cite news|title=‘Man of Steel’ Star Henry Cavill Eyes Lead in WB’s ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/man-of-steel-star-henry-cavill-eyes-lead-in-wbs-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-1200488719/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=variety.com|date=2013-05-28|archive-date=2013-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813065820/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/man-of-steel-star-henry-cavill-eyes-lead-in-wbs-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-1200488719/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Henry Cavill In Talks For ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’ Lead|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/henry-cavill-in-talks-for-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-lead/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2013-05-28|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019084809/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/henry-cavill-in-talks-for-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-lead/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月31日，[[伊莉莎白·戴比基|伊莉莎白·戴比基]]加入電影作為一個[[蛇蠍美人|蛇蠍美人]]類型的角色，在此之前[[蘿絲·拜恩|蘿絲·拜恩]]和[[莎莉·賽隆|莎莉·賽隆]]都是此角的考慮人選<ref name=Elizabeth>{{cite news|title=‘Great Gatsby’s’ Elizabeth Debicki Attracted to ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/great-gatsby-elizabeth-debicki-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-1200570367/|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=variety.com|date=2013-07-31|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130152340/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/great-gatsby-elizabeth-debicki-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-1200570367/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年8月8日，[[休·葛蘭|休·葛蘭]]加入劇組飾演「[[紳士局|紳士局]]」的領導者{{link-en|亞歷山大·威佛利|Alexander Waverly}}<ref name=Hugh>{{cite news|title=Hugh Grant Joins 'Man from U.N.C.L.E.'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hugh-grant-joins-man-uncle-602708|accessdate=2013-08-15|newspaper=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2013-08-08|archive-date=2013-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813163413/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hugh-grant-joins-man-uncle-602708|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年9月4日，[[傑瑞德·哈里斯|傑瑞德·哈里斯]]將飾演[[中情局|中情局]]的桑德斯<ref name="Jared">{{Cite web |url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/news/jared-harris-joins-man-uncle-619684 |title=Jared Harris Joins 'Man From U.N.C.L.E.' |access-date=2014-09-20 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924185548/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jared-harris-joins-man-uncle-619684 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{link-en|路卡·卡爾瓦尼|Luca Calvani}}飾演主要反派亞歷山德<ref name="Luca">{{cite news|title=Luca Calvani Lands Villain In ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.,’ Signs With Paradigm|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/luca-calvani-lands-villain-in-man-from-uncle-signs-with-paradigm/|accessdate=2013-09-13|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2013-09-12|archive-date=2013-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914135137/http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/luca-calvani-lands-villain-in-man-from-uncle-signs-with-paradigm/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{link-en|西蒙娜·卡帕里尼|Simona Caparrini}}飾演康提莎<ref name=Simona>{{cite news|title=Simona Caparrini Talks About Henry Cavill on Set of The Man From U.N.C.L.E.|url=http://henrycavill.org/en/exclusive/interviews-articles/item/917-simona-capparini-talks-about-henry-cavill-on-set-of-the-man-from-uncle?utm_content=buffer8741f&utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter.com&utm_campaign=buffer|newspaper=www.HenryCavill.org|date=2014-02-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921144617/http://henrycavill.org/en/exclusive/interviews-articles/item/917-simona-capparini-talks-about-henry-cavill-on-set-of-the-man-from-uncle?utm_content=buffer8741f&utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter.com&utm_campaign=buffer|archivedate=2017-09-21}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
電影於2013年9月9日開始主要拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=Production begins on 'The Man From U.N.C.L.E.'|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/325640/cbb/production-begins-on-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e|accessdate=2013-09-11|newspaper=gmanetwork.com|date=2013-09-11|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214826/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/325640/cbb/production-begins-on-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2013年10月25日，拍攝的地點包括在[[倫敦|倫敦]]格林威治皇家維多利亞碼頭的{{link-en|舊皇家海軍學院|Old Royal Naval College}}、英國[[西薩塞克斯郡|西薩塞克斯郡]]的{{link-en|古德伍德賽道|Goodwood Circuit}}。

