== 市場營銷 ==
據The Projection List網站，本片有望將於2015年2月13日的《[[金牌特務|金牌特務]]》播放前釋出首支預告<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://projectionlist.com/#/site/trailers |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112005246/http://projectionlist.com/#/site/trailers |archive-date=2015-01-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。然而，官方則提前於2月11日在網上釋出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/02/11/man-from-uncle-trailer|title=Henry Cavill and Armie Hammer partner up in exclusive The Man From U.N.C.L.E. trailer|access-date=2015-02-12|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108125133/https://ew.com/article/2015/02/11/man-from-uncle-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
本片先前的發布日期為2015年1月16日<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros Dates ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’ For 2015 MLK Weekend; Will Smith’s ‘Focus’ Set For February 2015|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/man-from-uncle-movie-release-date-january-15-2015-guy-ritchie/|accessdate=2014-02-21|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2014-02-20|archive-date=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424230836/http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/man-from-uncle-movie-release-date-january-15-2015-guy-ritchie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但於2014年8月12日，華納兄弟公司將上映日期延後至2015年8月14日<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros. Dates ‘American Sniper'; Moves ‘Point Break’, ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/08/american-sniper-clint-eastwood-man-from-uncle-point-break-release-dates-818516/|accessdate=2014-08-13|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-08-12|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162356/https://deadline.com/2014/08/american-sniper-clint-eastwood-man-from-uncle-point-break-release-dates-818516/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《紳士密令》整體獲得了正面良好的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據293條專業影評持有68%的新鮮度，平均得分6.2／10；該網站共識：「《紳士密令》試圖以充滿魅力的影星來詮釋一個平凡的故事和美得冒泡的組合，這加起來讓原不均衡的動作驚悚片稱得上完善，以克服其缺乏實質內容」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_man_from_uncle/|title=The Man from U.N.C.L.E.|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-08-11|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128124638/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_man_from_uncle|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得分56（滿分100），代表「好壞平均參雜」的評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-man-from-uncle|title=The Man from U.N.C.L.E. reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2015-08-11|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113145827/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-man-from-uncle|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾從A +至F的評級中給予本片「B」的評價<ref name="Opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/straight-outta-compton-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-weekend-box-office-1201499183/|title=‘Compton’ Rivals Previous August Tentpoles With $22.8M Friday; ‘U.N.C.L.E.’ Shows Gray Hair – Late Night B.O.|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|publisher=(Penske Media Corporation)|date=2015-08-15|accessdate=2015-08-15|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214065932/https://deadline.com/2015/08/straight-outta-compton-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-weekend-box-office-1201499183/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

